# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MCP Sentinel — Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy to .env and fill in values:  cp .env.example .env
# The Makefile auto-loads .env and exports all variables.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# GitHub personal access token (used by python-semantic-release)
# Scopes needed: repo (for pushing tags and creating releases)
GH_TOKEN=

# Snyk API token (optional — only needed if not already authenticated via `snyk auth`)
# Get yours at: https://app.snyk.io/account
# SNYK_TOKEN=
